description:
Welcome,

My name is John and I love the outdoors.  I love to explore new places and take in the sights.  My channel will be primarily about mountain biking and the new trails I will encounter along the way.  But I am also going to post my life's adventures.

I am near the end of my career and will be retiring in three years.  My plan is to become a full-time RV'r, travel the country and explore this wonderful nation and take you along the way.  

I am lucky to have a wonderful girlfriend who encourages me to travel and mtb.  I also have the benefit of getting to  travel the country.  Last year I got to go to California, New York, Texas and Las Vegas.  I even flew to Dallas just for lunch.

Please come along and enjoy my travels to include Snow Skiing, Hiking, Motorcycle Riding, and any events I attend.  Also mainly MTBing.

description:
When I was a young boy (1950's), I learned to play golf by closely watching the best players at the course I grew up on. I would then stand in front of a window and copy their swings... then I would go to the practice area to ingrain that look and new feeling to muscle memory. That WAS and STILL IS a great way to learn! It's called SELF-DISCOVERY! 

When you discover a helpful motion or thought ALL BY YOURSELF, YOU WILL NEVER FORGET IT! - I never have!  

At the age of 78, I'm still a mid single-digit player. My goal with this YouTube channel is to provide a platform for TEACHING and LEARNING! I will provide videos and detailed descriptions of the finest golfers in the world, their swings and some of their finest shots so YOU can learn and improve as I have. 

The focus here is geared toward TEACHING and LEARNING the short game (putting, chipping, pitching and wedge play from 120-yards in), but you will also see some of the finest, Tour-Proven full swings and descriptions as well.⛳️

description:
Valentina Schulz é paulista, tem 17 anos e participou do 1º MasterChef Junior, transmitido pela Rede Bandeirantes de Televisão.

Apesar de ter a culinária como hobby, sonha em ser atriz e apresentadora, por isso estuda teatro e técnicas de atuação desde 2011. Também é apaixonada por psicologia, neurociência e moda.

Em 2016 foi eleita melhor Muser de Transição pelo Musical.ly/Tik Tok. Já foi palestrante em eventos como  Path, Wired e YouPix e creator oficial da CCXP em 2017, 2018 e 2019. Foi apresentadora e finalista do Meus Prêmios Nick 2017, finalista do Teen Choice Awards 2018 e vencedora do Prêmio Capricho 2017.

Lançou seu primeiro livro: Diário da Valen em 2018 na Bienal do Livro de SP.

Recentemente estreou em seu canal o "Escuta Só!", em parceria com Fernanda Concon, MC Soffia e Mary Chagas. O programa, que mistura debates e entretenimento, foi criado por Valentina e pelo diretor Christiano Metri, que também é responsável pela direção geral. A produção é da Piloto.

Gatan is the world’s leading manufacturer of instrumentation and software used to enhance and extend the operation and performance of electron microscopes. Gatan products, which are fully compatible with nearly all electron microscope models, cover the entire range of the research process–from specimen preparation and manipulation to imaging and analysis. The Gatan brand name is recognized and respected throughout the worldwide scientific community and has been synonymous with high-quality products and leading technology for more than 50 years. Gatan is headquartered in Pleasanton, California, USA. For more information, visit www.gatan.com.

Gatan works with academic and industry researchers to push the boundaries of what can be done with electron microscopy. Together, we have invented new approaches to problems that deliver fresh understanding, plus facilitate advancements in materials, life science, electronics, and natural resources research.

Pan. Tilt. Zoom.
Livestreaming Solutions

What is a PTZ Camera?
A PTZ camera is a pan, tilt, and zoom robotic video camera controllable by a remote operator to pan horizontally, tilt vertically & diagonally, and zoom in on a subject to enhance the image quality without digital pixilation. These cameras are designed to make broadcast-quality video affordable. They allow for an easy, automated production workflow with other software technologies for recording and live streaming directly to content delivery networks like Facebook and YouTube.

PTZOptics is a broadcast, live streaming and conference camera manufacturer operating out of Downingtown, Pennsylvania, USA. We provide Pan Tilt Zoom Cameras with HDMI, HD-SDI, USB 3.0 and IP Streaming at resolutions up to 1080p60fps for the professional broadcast and video conferencing markets.

mGSM.pl jest serwisem zajmującym się szeroko pojętą tematyką GSM, ale skupiającym się przede wszystkim na najbardziej namacalnych i powszechnie dostępnych tej technologii przejawach - na telefonach komórkowych.

Byliśmy przy narodzinach technologii mobilnych w Polsce, współtworzyliśmy rynek, a jako serwis internetowy poświęcony telefonom istniejemy od 2005 roku - i od tej pory staramy się dostarczyć użytkownikom Internetu jak najbardziej rzetelną informację o specyfikacji technicznej dostępnych na rynku urządzeń. Nasze dane są oparte na dokumentacji producentów i ilustrowane, jeśli to tylko możliwe, dużymi oficjalnymi zdjęciami prasowymi poszczególnych modeli.

Na mGSM.pl można nie tylko porównać poszczególne modele, czy odnaleźć testy telefonów i aktualności ze światka GSM, ale również wypowiedzieć się o posiadanym telefonie i znaleźć pomocną dłoń dzięki systemowi moderowanych komentarzy.

Doberman dysponuje ponadprzeciętnym węchem, bystrym, wręcz analitycznym umysłem, spokojnym acz zdecydowanym charakterem, niesamowitym oddaniem jeśli tylko nie zaznał od właściciela przemocy. Uczy się bardzo szybko, tylko trzeba być niesamowicie konsekwentnym, a jednocześnie słuchającym psa i zacząć szkolenie jak najszybciej. Ustalić zasady, które są nie do złamania, nawet jeśli my będziemy mieli słabszy dzień.( Ty przechodzisz pierwszy przez drzwi, Ty rządzisz jego miską zawsze, Ty wyznaczasz czas i miejsce na zabawę, Ty nie łasisz się o jego uwagę, nie podchodzisz i nie pieścisz się z pieskiem gdy on spokojnie leży, bo o pieszczoty w stadzie, skomlą słabsze jednostki tylko, a nie chcesz za taką uchodzić) No, zabrakło miejsca :-)

description:
Turns out that I wasn't rendering my videos correctly. I was leaving extraneous frames left over from interpolation in pretty much all my videos and also the my output FPS was slightly off. So I decided I would redo all my videos since there's not that many and only a few have a lot of views. This time I will make sure to not make these dumb mistakes.
I am going to stick to 60 FPS because that's the most common refresh rate on current monitors and TVs.
The 4 primary software I will be using will be Sony Vegas 12, GoPro Studio, Hybrid and Freemake Video converter.
I believe in HFR for all video content. Message me if you want to see any particular video at a higher frame rate!
